      "supporting_terms": ["Regime change agenda", "Operation Epic Fury"]
    }
  ],
  "confidence_notes": "Analysis relies on NPR affiliate reporting but notes: 1) Some casualty figures come from Iranian state media (IRNA). 2) Target verification (e.g., Khamenei status) remains unconfirmed. 3) No independent verification of nuclear threat claims. 4) Limited perspective from Iranian officials beyond Foreign Ministry statements."
}

